# Your papers and PDFs go here. NOT tracked in Git, on purpose:
#   - Copyrighted work should not be pushed to GitHub.
#   - PDFs bloat the repo and eat your storage.
#
# Your library of record is Zotero, not this folder. On a new machine, just
# recreate an empty literature/ folder; re-export or re-download from Zotero
# as needed. Nothing here syncs through Git by design.
